{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "budgetbuddy-api-2024",
		"name": "BudgetBuddy API",
		"description": "Complete API collection for BudgetBuddy - Personal Finance Management System\n\n## Features\n- 🔐 Authentication (Cookie + Bearer Token)\n- 🔐 Two-Factor Authentication (TOTP)\n- 💰 Accounts Management\n- 📊 Transactions & Transfers\n- 💼 Budgets & Categories\n- 🏷️ Category Types\n- 💱 Currencies\n- 📈 Investments & Portfolio\n- 📉 Reports & Analytics\n- 📈 Dashboard\n- ⚙️ User Settings\n- 🔔 Budget Alerts\n- 🔒 Security Events (Admin)\n- 📋 Audit History (Admin)\n- 🏥 Health Checks\n- 🔄 Idempotency Support\n\n## Setup\n1. Set `baseUrl` variable to your API URL (default: https://localhost:5001)\n2. Login using `/auth/login` endpoint\n3. Copy the access token to `bearerToken` variable\n4. Start testing!\n\n## Variables\n- `baseUrl`: API base URL\n- `bearerToken`: JWT access token\n- `accountId`, `categoryId`, `categoryTypeId`, `transactionId`, `budgetId`, `investmentId`: Created resource IDs",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
		"_exporter_id": "budgetbuddy"
	},
	"auth": {
		"type": "bearer",
		"bearer": [
			{
				"key": "token",
				"value": "{{bearerToken}}",
				"type": "string"
			}
		]
	},
	"variable": [
		{
			"key": "baseUrl",
			"value": "https://localhost:5001",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "bearerToken",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		},
